commentTextItems.html: full toss, Taylor hits it high and over the midwicket fence for maximum

commentPostTextItems.html: The crowd goes crazy, every one excited, school children dancing, wonderful strike from Taylor to get the winning runs, scoring 79 runs in 72 balls.
A great win for Zimbabwe, winning of the final delivery. Zimbabwe win by 2 wickets. Taylor was well supported by Mupariwa. For Bangladesh Shahadat Hossain picked up a hat-trick.
That's it from here, it was exciting bringing you the live commentary, I am Binoy George signing off. Please join us for the 4th ODI on August 4th. Until then it Bye from all of us here at Cricinfo.
